{"id": 2893, "genre": 1001, "title": "哪些时刻你会有“自己的生活被同一家公司包办”的感觉？", "description": "不知不觉中，被“大厂”们承包的生活细节是越来越多了。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA Images）", "record_count": 1693, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190410132236AutKmq7bZofN2RCh.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-04-15T03:00:48Z", "options": [{"id": 339261, "content": "从超贵的保养品到最普通日用产品同属一家公司", "image": null, "praise_count": 125, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1590940}, {"id": 339263, "content": "我没记错的话。。淘宝是马云的，微博 是马云的，支付宝是马云的。（手动微笑）", "image": null, "praise_count": 158, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 972975}, {"id": 339264, "content": "护肤品清一色雅诗兰黛，而且也不想换牌子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1626108}, {"id": 339521, "content": "哪里都是买卖，愈发觉得孤独", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1639423}, {"id": 339266, "content": "当我发现很久没有打开微博，在微信中可以获得一切消息的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 116463}, {"id": 339267, "content": "真的这样很累", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1164967}, {"id": 339268, "content": "打开手机的时候，两个大厂包办了，最好把我的婚姻包办了，哈哈哈哈！", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 515073}, {"id": 339269, "content": "戴森全家桶", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115890}, {"id": 339270, "content": "一定要用钉钉，微信不行", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1294190}, {"id": 339271, "content": "被我认为是死对头的哇哈哈和爽歪歪竟同属一家公司", "image": null, "praise_count": 71, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497141}, {"id": 339272, "content": "宝洁", "image": null, "praise_count": 98, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1599974}, {"id": 339273, "content": "支付宝微信已经包办一切", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1275977}, {"id": 339274, "content": "未来好可怕", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1525237}, {"id": 339275, "content": "手机办卡，选择各种流量包套餐时。阿里系、腾讯系、头条系、百度系、网易系……", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1563969}, {"id": 339276, "content": "玩的游戏基本被两个公司包圆儿了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1567722}, {"id": 339277, "content": "小米+腾讯+阿里=包办一切", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 917047}, {"id": 339278, "content": "无时无刻的工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1230250}, {"id": 339279, "content": "好奇心不是腾讯的 那不就没包圆吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 82, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 535937}, {"id": 339280, "content": "Qdaily也被腾讯收购的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1571537}, {"id": 339281, "content": "未来会是绿洲吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1638457}, {"id": 339283, "content": "……每个城市都有那么几个大型超市", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1633378}, {"id": 339539, "content": "手机，耳机，背包，充电宝，都是魅族。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252704}, {"id": 339285, "content": "支付宝 渗透到生活各处……连医院体检都可以用支付宝", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1636316}, {"id": 339797, "content": "当我拿起牙膏，发现宝洁的；拿起香皂，宝洁的，拿起洗头水，宝洁的；洗衣服时，宝洁的洗衣液；刷碗时用洗洁精，宝洁的；最后想，我拖地吧，看着拖布把熟悉的宝洁logo，不由得热泪盈眶", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1633295}, {"id": 339286, "content": "阿里和腾讯包办了一切衣食住行，可怕", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359635}, {"id": 339287, "content": "微信小程序", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1450211}, {"id": 339288, "content": "用Google账号登录所有的国外网站", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1334247}, {"id": 339290, "content": "什么都不用说了，都是党国的", "image": null, "praise_count": 84, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 391490}, {"id": 339292, "content": "手机里常用的APP是字节系", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1638516}, {"id": 339294, "content": "P&G\n联合利华", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1424243}, {"id": 339295, "content": "Adobe全家桶", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1424243}, {"id": 339296, "content": "家电，生活用品，食品基本就那么几家品牌", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377475}, {"id": 339297, "content": "希望尽快用上苹果全家桶哈哈哈。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 695459}, {"id": 339300, "content": "工作的公司 宿舍附近的地下卖场 公司附近的购物中心 以及邻城的购物中心 都属于同一家公司", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1427707}, {"id": 339303, "content": "一个阿里定向流量包就全搞定了🤔", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1555010}, {"id": 339559, "content": "洗浴用品\nP&G宝洁", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147315}, {"id": 339304, "content": "在发展多几年，大公司完全垄断个人信息，就很赛博朋克了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1599456}, {"id": 346225, "content": "腾讯系、阿里系", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1661020}, {"id": 339317, "content": "白天公司上班，晚上公司宿舍，吃饭公司食堂，上班公司班车，散步公司园区。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597047}, {"id": 339834, "content": "Apple全家系列～😅", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1640248}, {"id": 339325, "content": "暂时没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1597827}, {"id": 340105, "content": "漫威居然是迪士尼旗下！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1581555}, {"id": 340107, "content": "刺客信条，幽灵行动，彩虹六号，细胞分裂，看门狗，全境封锁，纪元，酷飙车神，荣耀战魂", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1020253}, {"id": 339854, "content": "蓝厂和绿厂居然是一家", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1633083}, {"id": 339343, "content": "淘宝", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1580555}, {"id": 339601, "content": "XX银行，XX石油，XX移动，腾讯最大股东XX", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1370300}, {"id": 339350, "content": "从小到大，小时候奶奶用婴儿润肤乳，中学用可伶可俐，大学用城野医生，最近才知道全是强生的，感冒吃的泰诺也是强生的…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1638637}, {"id": 339351, "content": "腾讯呀，常用的软件都有它的股份", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147717}, {"id": 339609, "content": "当微信可以支付，QQ可以联系\n我就觉得腾讯已经开始包办我的生活了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1439825}, {"id": 339356, "content": "逛街的地方都是在北京路", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1638647}]}